#Cybersecurity

Common cyber attack vectors:

  • Malware
  • email attachments
  • Webpages
  • pop-up window
  • instant messages (IMs)
  • Chatrooms
  • Human element
  • SQL injection ; DROP TABLE USERS
  • Wireless communication
  • sniffing (bluetooth, wireless, etc.)
  • Social engineering
